rtment%20in%202017%20and%20produces%20a%20beautifully%20designed%20loafer%20that's%20handmade%20in%20Portugal%20using%20top-of-the-line%20materials%20and%20Goodyear%20welting%20so%20they%20can%20easily%20be%20resoled%20when%20needed.%20These%20shoes%20were%20easy%20to%20break%20in%2C%20are%20super%20comfortable%2C%20and%20feature%20a%20lug%20sole%20for%20a%20bit%20more%20edge%20that'll%20easily%20up%20your%20style%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20I%20style%20loafers%20for%20men%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBeauty%20is%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20beholder%2C%20and%20that's%20certainly%20true%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20popular%20brands%20making%20some%20of%20the%20best%20loafers%20for%20men.%20Loafers%20can%20be%20styled%20plenty%20of%20different%20ways%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20classics%3A%20They%20work%20very%20well%20as%20a%20dress%20shoe%20alternative%20alongside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-mens-comfortable-performance-workwear-brands-for-office%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomfortable%20men's%20workwear%3C%2Fa%3E%20(like%20chinos%2C%20a%20well-fitting%20polo%20or%20an%20Oxford%20shirt%2C%20and%20a%20cotton%20blazer).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaintaining%20a%20crisp%2C%20cleaned-up%20loafer%20with%20the%20help%20of%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-shoe-polish%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20shoe%20polish%3C%2Fa%3E%20gives%20you%20a%20pair%20of%20work%20shoes%20you%20can%20confidently%20wear%20to%20the%20office.%20If%20your%20pair%20has%20a%20sneaker-like%20sole%20or%20a%20more%20casual%20nubuck%20leather%2C%20they%20can%20work%20in%20place%20of%20sneakers%20with%20chino%20shorts%20and%20a%20pocket%20tee%20for%20a%20touch%20of%20high-low%2C%20laidback%20prep%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20wear%20your%20loafers%20for%20formal%20events%2C%20like%20with%20a%20light%20cotton%20or%20linen%20suit%20to%20an%20outdoor%20summer%20wedding.%20And%20in%20a%20final%20show%20of%20versatility%2C%20a%20more%20casual%20style%20of%20loafer%20can%20be%20paired%20with%20rolled%20dark%20blue%20jeans%20and%20an%20Oxford%20shirt%20or%20well-fitting%20polo%20%E2%80%93%20off%20the%20clock%2C%20cold%20beer%20in%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20I%20choose%20the%20best%20pair%20of%20loafers%20for%20men%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChoosing%20the%20best%20loafers%20for%20men%20is%20a%20fun%20quest%20all%20its%20own%2C%20but%20it%20requires%20focusing%20on%20how%20you%20plan%20to%20wear%20them.%20If%20you%20want%20an%20alternative%20to%20dress%20shoes%2C%20opt%20for%20a%20pair%20from%20a%20brand%20that%20uses%20a%20dress%20shoe-esque%20design%20to%20create%20a%20streamlined%2C%20sharp%20pair%20of%20loafers%20ready%20for%20both%20the%20office%20and%20a%20classy%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20there%20are%20companies%20making%20more%20sporty%20driving%20loafers%2C%20like%20Greats%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20grippy%20design%20you%20can%20wear%20behind%20the%20wheel%20of%20a%20car.%20Amberjack's%20use%20of%20sneaker%20technology%20in%20modern%20loafers%20with%20next-level%20comfort%20make%20them%20well-suited%20for%20plenty%20of%20casual%20style%20situations.%20The%20right%20loafers%20should%20fit%20your%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20by%20choosing%20wisely%2C%20you'll%20have%20a%20wardrobe%20staple%20to%20rely%20on%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-loafers-men%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757013104000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b7316f194a2d49b8af9198%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-loafers-men%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20loafers%20for%20men%20can%20be%2