savings.%20Before%20its%20merger%20with%20Skydance%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-laying-off-3-5-percent-of-us-staff-memo-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EParamount%20cut%203.5%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20its%20US%20workforce%20in%20June%20amid%20the%20decline%20of%20the%20linear%20TV%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllison%20said%20the%20return%20would%20start%20in%20January%20with%20employees%20based%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20New%20York.%20Starting%20this%20month%2C%20severance%20would%20be%20offered%20to%20those%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0at%20levels%20of%20VP%20and%20below%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0who%20can't%20or%20don't%20want%20to%20return%20full%20time%2C%20with%20some%20limited%20exceptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20in-person%20collaboration%20is%20absolutely%20vital%20to%20building%20and%20strengthening%20our%20culture%20and%20driving%20the%20success%20of%20our%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20wrote%20in%20a%20memo%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20have%20had%20various%20reactions%20to%20the%20news.%20One%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they'd%20have%20to%20leave%20the%20company%20because%20they%20couldn't%20move%20to%20New%20York%20for%20family%20reasons.%20Another%20said%20as%20a%20single%20person%20with%20no%20kids%2C%20they%20didn't%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20people%20who%20don't%20live%20near%20NYC%20or%20LA%20and%20international%20contractors%20are%20worried%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20know%20how%20they%20are%20going%20to%20handle%20that%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20person%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllison%2C%20along%20with%20his%20father%2C%20Oracle%20billionaire%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flarry-ellison%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELarry%20Ellison%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recently%20took%20control%20of%20Paramount%20Global%20from%20Shari%20Redstone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Ellison%20has%20said%20he%20plans%20to%20revive%20the%20storied%20entertainment%20company%20with%20a%20tech%20infusion%20and%20other%20changes.%20He's%20moved%20fast%2C%20agreeing%20to%20a%20%247.7%20billion%20deal%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-ufc-rights-tko-deal-david-ellison-netflix-streaming-wars-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erights%20to%20the%20UFC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Shortly%20before%20the%20merger%20closed%2C%20Paramount%20did%20a%20%241.5%20billion%20deal%20with%20the%20creators%20of%20%26quot%3BSouth%20Park.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorporate%20America%20has%20gradually%20been%20rolling%20back%20pandemic-era%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-requiring-return-to-office-rto-mandate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eremote%20work%20policies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20Paramount%20Skydance's%20move%20goes%20further%20than%20many%20of%20its%20media%20and%20entertainment%20peers.%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%20has%20called%20people%20back%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20while%20Disney%20has%20mandated%20a%20four-day%20return%20for%20many%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20had%2018%2C600%20employees%20as%20of%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20according%20to%20its%20filings%20with%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20Ellison's%20full%20memo%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EDear%20Team%2C%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20believe%20that%20in-person%20collaboration%20is%20absolutely%20vital%20to%20building%20and%20strengthening%20our%20culture%20and%20driving%20the%20success%20of%20our%20business.%20Our%20people%20are%20the%20key%20to%20winning%2C%20and%20being%20together%20helps%20us%20innovate%2C%20solve%20problems%2C%20share%20ideas%2C%20create%2C%20challenge%20one%20another%2C%20and%20build%20the%20relationships%20that%20will%20make%20this%20company%20great.%20As%20I%20said%20during%20our%20town%20hall%2C%20some%20of%20the%20most%20formative%20moments%20of%20my%20life%20happened%20in%20rooms%20where%20I%20was%20a%20fly%20on%20the%20wall%2C%20listening%20and%20learning.%20I've%20never%20seen%20that%20happen%20on%20Zoom.%20Being%20together%20in-person%20isn't%20just%20about%20showing%20up%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20about%20actively%20engaging%20with%20the%20business%2C%20supporting%20one%20another%20and%20the%20team's%20efforts%2C%20and%20contributing%20to%20our%20shared%20momentum.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ETo%20achieve%20what%20we've%20set%20out%20to%20do%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20truly%20unlock%20Paramount's%20full%20potential%20%E2%80%94%20we%20must%20make%20meaningful%20changes%20that%20position%20us%20for%20long-term%20success.%20These%20changes%20are%20about%20building%20a%20stronger%2C%20more%20connected%2C%20and%20agile%20organization%20that%20can%20deliver%20on%20our%20goals%20and%20compete%20at%20the%20highest%20level.%20We%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20accomplish%20and%20we're%20moving%20fast.%20We%20need%20to%20all%20be%20rowing%20in%20the%20same%20direction.%20And%20especially%20when%20you're%20dealing%20with%20a%20creative%20business%20like%20ours%2C%20that%20begins%20with%20being%20together%20in%20person.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWith%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20we%20will%20begin%20a%20phased%20return-to-office%20plan%20starting%20in%20January%202026%2C%20ultimately%20moving%20towards%20an%20in-person%20work%20environment%20where%20employees%20are%20in%20the%20office%20full-time%20(five%20days%20a%20week).%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EHere's%20what%20to%20expect%3A%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EPhase%20One%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Beginning%20January%205%2C%202026%2C%20employees%20assigned%20to%20our%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20New%20York%20offices%20will%20return%20to%20full-time%20office%20work.%20We%20understand%20that%20some%20people%20may%20not%20choose%20or%20be%20able%20to%20make%20this%20transition.%20And%20so%2C%20starting%20today%20through%20September%2015%2C%202025%2C%20we%20will%20be%20offering%20a%20severance%20opt-in%20program%20for%20VPs%20and%20below%2C%20based%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20New%20York%2C%20who%20cannot%20or%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20return%20full-time.%20Details%20will%20be%20shared%20directly%20with%20those%20eligible.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EPhase%20Two%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20In%202026%2C%20we%20will%20announce%20plans%20for%20employees%20not%20assigned%20to%20our%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20New%20York%20offices%2C%20including%20international%20offices%20and%20those%20originally%20hired%20into%20fully%20remote%20roles.%20VPs%20and%20below%20in%20Phase%20Two%20will%20be%20eligible%20for%20a%20similar%20opt-in%20program%20and%20will%20receive%20details%20at%20a%20later%20date.%20We%20will%20be%20adopting%20this%20same%20approach%20in%20our%20international%20offices%20and%20will%20roll%20out%20the%20specific%20plans%20in%20accordance%20with%20our%20local%20legal%20obligations.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWe%20recognize%20this%20represents%20a%20significant%20change%20for%20many%2C%20and%20we're%20committed%20to%20supporting%20you%20throughout%20this%20transition.%20We%20will%20work%20closely%20with%20managers%20to%20ensure%20you%20have%20the%20time%20and%20flexibility%20to%20make%20the%20necessary%20adjustments.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EFor%20more%20details%2C%20please%20log%20into%20Okta%20to%20visit%20our%20%3Cstrong%3EFAQ%20page%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20If%20you%20don't%20find%20what%20you%20need%2C%20you%20can%20submit%20additional%20questions%20to%20our%20%3Cstrong%3EAskHR%20team%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThank%20you%20for%20your%20patience%2C%20adaptability%2C%20and%20continued%20dedication.%20Together%2C%20we%20are%20building%20a%20company%20that%20is%20stronger%2C%20more%20innovative%2C%20and%20ready%20to%20win.%20The%20opportunity%20ahead%20is%20extraordinary%2C%20and%20I'm%20confident%20that%20working%20side%20by%20side%2C%20we%20will%20achieve%20great%20things.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EBest%2C%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EDavid%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E**%20Certain%20union%20and%20non-union%20employees%20are%20ineligible%20for%20the%20opt-in%20severance%20program%2C%20including%E2%80%94but%20not%20limited%20to%E2%80%94those%20who%20work%20full-time%20onsite%2C%20are%20under%20contract%2C%20are%20non-staff%20or%20are%20part%20of%20the%20production%20workforce%20(including%20video%20game%20production).%20Additionally%2C%20they%20may%20also%20be%20subject%20to%20different%20return%20to%20office%20expectations%2C%20which%20will%20be%20shared%20separately.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-skydance-staff-back-five-days-week-memo-david-ellison-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757012967000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b9d53b57d362d375e78897%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-skydance-staff-back-five-days-week-memo-david-ellison-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CEO%20David%20Ellison%20said%20the%20return%20would%20start%20in%20January%20with%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20New%20York%2C%20with%20severance%20offered%20to%20those%20who%20don't%20return%20full%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmoses%40insider.com%20(Lucia%20Moses%2CJames%20Faris)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A106%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-skydance-staff-back-five-days-week-memo-david-ellison-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Argentina%20Charges%20Nazi's%20Daughter%20For%20Hiding%20Decades-Old%20Art%20Theft%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20daughter%20and%20son-in-law%20of%20a%20Nazi%20who%20stole%20art%20from%20European%20Jews%20during%20World%20War%20II%20were%20charged%20in%20an%20Argentine%20court%20Thursday%20with%20hiding%20numerous%20works%2C%20including%2022%20by%