mber%2030%20to%20qualify%20for%20federal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgood-time-buy-electric-car-before-ev-tax-credit-expires-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEV%20tax%20credits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20axed%20as%20part%20of%20his%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-passes-big-beautiful-bill-trump-signing-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Beautiful%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20The%20tax%20and%20spending%20bill%2C%20passed%20by%20Congress%20in%20July%2C%20eliminated%20a%20%247%2C500%20tax%20credit%20for%20new%20EVs%20and%20a%20%244%2C000%20tax%20credit%20for%20used%20EVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20is%20a%20blow%20to%20American%20EV%20manufacturers%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fall-the-evs-set-to-lose-the-federal-tax-credit-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20could%20see%20a%20drop%20in%20sales%20as%20drivers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fslate-auto-ceo-jeff-bezos-backed-ev-startup-cheap-pickup-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereconsider%20the%20higher%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20some%20automakers%20say%20they%20expect%20a%20temporary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ford-push-sell-more-evs-before-tax-credit-ends-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboost%20in%20EV%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20people%20race%20to%20use%20the%20tax%20credits%20before%20they're%20officially%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%20before%20the%20deadline%20hits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22492ca8ce-7863-4a48-960b-217528825130%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20qualifies%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fcredits-deductions%2Fcredits-for-new-clean-vehicles-purchased-in-2023-or-after%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIRS%20says%20drivers%20may%20qualify%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20an%20EV%20tax%20credit%20of%20up%20to%20%247%2C500%20if%20they%20purchase%20a%20new%2C%20qualified%20plug-in%20EV%20or%20fuel%20cell%20electric%20vehicle.%20Drivers%20can't%20buy%20the%20EV%20for%20resale%20and%20must%20use%20it%20primarily%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20a%20driver's%20modified%20adjusted%20gross%20income%20cannot%20exceed%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%24300%2C000%20for%20married%20couples%20filing%20jointly%20or%20a%20surviving%20spouse%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%24225%2C000%20for%20heads%20of%20households%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%24150%2C000%20for%20all%20other%20filers%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22231e83a1-e986-4b81-8a92-45985e06c043%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20vehicles%20qualify%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IRS%20says%20a%20qualifying%20EV%20vehicle%20must%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHave%20a%20battery%20capacity%20of%20at%20least%207%20kilowatt%20hours%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHave%20a%20gross%20vehicle%20weight%20rating%20of%20less%20than%2014%2C000%20pounds%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBe%20made%20by%20a%20qualified%20manufacturer%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUndergo%20final%20assembly%20in%20North%20America%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeet%20critical%20mineral%20and%20battery%20component%20requirements%20(as%20of%20April%2018%2C%202023)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2288726711-80e4-4693-abad-1ca195e9a170%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20you%20still%20qualify%20for%20EV%20tax%20credits%20if%20you%20purchase%20a%20contract%20by%20September%2030%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20short%20answer%20is%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAcquiring%20a%20vehicle%20prior%20to%20the%20termination%20date%20is%20an%20initial%20step%2C%20but%20acquisition%20alone%20does%20not%20immediately%20entitle%20a%20taxpayer%20to%20a%20credit%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IRS%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20car%20must%20also%20be%20%26quot%3Bplaced%20in%20service%26quot%3B%20to%20claim%20the%20credit%2C%20the%20IRS%20says.%20That%20just%20means%20you%20can%20only%20claim%20the%20credit%20after%20you%20have%20the%20car%20in%20your%20possession%2C%20and%20it's%20OK%20if%20that's%20after%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20taxpayer%20acquires%20a%20vehicle%20by%20having%20a%20written%20binding%20contract%20in%20place%20and%20a%20payment%20made%20on%20or%20before%20September%2030%2C%202025%2C%20then%20the%20taxpayer%20will%20be%20entitled%20to%20claim%20the%20credit%20when%20they%20place%20the%20vehicle%20in%20service%20(namely%2C%20when%20they%20take%20possession%20of%20the%20vehicle)%2C%20even%20if%20the%20vehicle%20is%20placed%20in%20service%20after%20September%2030%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-tax-credit-end-what-to-know-tesla-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757007640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b9c0fd32af4d666ef73f25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-tax-credit-end-what-to-know-tesla-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Drivers%20in%20the%20US%20have%20until%20September%2030%20to%20qualify%20for%20federal%20EV%20tax%20credits%2C%20which%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20axed%20as%20part%20of%20his%20%26quot%3BBig%20Beautiful%20Bill.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-tax-credit-end-what-to-know-tesla-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UTI%20AMC%20elevates%20CIO%20Subramaniam%20as%20CEO%3B%20Bandhan%20AMC%20set%20for%20SIF%20foray%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757007449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-01%2F12%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X630%2F1736680723-27