ne.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20non-football%20fan%2C%20this%20might%20seem%20incredibly%20inconsequential.%20(It%20is.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Faustinkarp%2Fstatus%2F1963655822778527881%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DxhuXMba3HM4poWm9CQq-PA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20one%20media%20reporter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20will%20only%20be%20four%2015-second%20commercials%20during%20the%20entire%20broadcast%2C%20and%20football%20will%20remain%20on%20the%20screen%20the%20entire%20time.)%20But%20it's%20about%20more%20than%20terrible%20insurance%20and%20car%20commercials%20invading%20my%20Sunday%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20it's%20another%20example%20of%20the%20NFL%20flexing%20its%20business%20muscles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20initial%20online%20uproar%2C%20most%20fans%20aren't%20going%20anywhere.%20After%20all%2C%20it's%20the%20NFL's%20world%2C%20and%20we're%20just%20living%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20NFL%20vet%20Chris%20Long%20described%20the%20league's%20dominance%20on%20his%20podcast%20%26quot%3BGreen%20Light%26quot%3B%20this%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NFL%20is%20an%20apex%20predator%2C%20and%20right%20now%20what%20it's%20doing%20is%20it's%20eating%20other%20people's%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDJuIYnCBB8w%2F%3Figsh%3DdGhhZjI2Y2Jjcmx6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20two-time%20Super%20Bowl%20champ%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cdbcad3d-9c99-4591-af0a-83f51e483f61%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommercials%20were%20always%20the%20long%20game%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20honest%2C%20the%20commercial%20writing%20has%20been%20on%20RedZone's%20walls%20for%20a%20while.%20As%20the%20program's%20popularity%20has%20grown%20since%20its%202009%20launch%2C%20people%20have%20pondered%20when%20the%20NFL%20would%20let%20advertisers%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20already%20features%20plenty%20of%20sponsorships%2C%20but%20stopped%20short%20of%20full-on%20commercials%2C%20save%20for%20a%20brief%20trial%20run%20late%20last%20year.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FScottHanson%2Fstatus%2F1870279812440330688%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%20were%20NOT%20happy%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20deal%20with%20ESPN%20earlier%20this%20year%20led%20to%20speculation%20commercials%20would%20soon%20follow.%20However%2C%20you%20can't%20blame%20the%20Mouse%20House%20for%20this%20one.%20That%20deal%20isn't%20finalized%2C%20and%20the%20league%20told%20sports%20media%20reporter%20Richard%20Deitsch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fricharddeitsch%2Fstatus%2F1963352048151187865%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20had%20been%20contemplating%20bringing%20commercials%20to%20RedZone%20for%20over%20a%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20not%20alone.%20Ads%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ads-took-over-streaming-tv-and-prediction-2025-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecoming%20the%20norm%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20most%20streamers%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20you%20think%20about%20it%2C%20did%20you%20expect%20anything%20else%20from%20the%20NFL%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211324ddc-e7ef-4652-8d9c-6b6ecaf94818%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20NFL%20is%20on%20a%20tear%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20due%20respect%20to%20Wall%20Street%20sharks%20and%20Big%20Tech%20giants%2C%20the%20NFL%20might%20be%20the%20most%20aggressive%20business%20on%20the%20block.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Philadelphia%20Eagles%20hang%20another%20championship%20banner%20tonight%20as%20they%20open%20the%20NFL%20season%20against%20the%20Dallas%20Cowboys%2C%20but%20the%20league%20holds%20the%20real%20crown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20colleague%20Peter%20Kafka%20has%20covered%20extensively%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fpeter-kafka%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eif%20you're%20not%20reading%20him%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20what%20are%20you%20doing%3F%20%E2%80%94%20NFL%20games%20remain%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-nfl-deal-shows-who-owns-tv-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehottest%20ticket%20in%20streaming%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompetition%20to%20broadcast%20NFL%20games%20has%20become%20a%20feeding%20frenzy.%20Networks%20and%20streamers%20have%20shelled%20out%20big%20bucks%20for%20the%20opportunity%20to%20air%20games.%20That's%20much%20to%20the%20league's%20delight%20and%20its%20fans'%20chagrin%2C%20who%20complain%20about%20the%20laundry%20list%20of%20subscriptions%20they%20need%20to%20watch%20all%20the%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20not%20going%20to%20get%20better.%20The%20NFL-Disney%20deal%20means%20the%20league%20will%20have%20four%20more%20games%20to%20sell%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-nfl-deal-shows-who-owns-tv-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20Peter%20noted%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20could%20mean%20even%20more%20subscriptions%20and%20demonstrates%20the%20league's%20expertise%20in%20maximizing%20profit%20from%20its%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NFL%20has%20also%20benefited%20from%20legalized%20sports%20gambling%20from%20a%20financial%20and%20viewership%20perspective.%20A%20meaningless%20Thursday%20night%20game%20becomes%20much%20more%20exciting%20when%20you%20cook%20up%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-flutter-fanduel-same-game-parlay-changed-us-sports-betting-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esame-game%20parlay%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20other%20leagues'%20star%20players%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-more-betting-scandals-are-pervading-us-sports-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecaught%20up%20in%20gambling%20controversies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20NFL%20hasn't%20had%20a%20reported%20issue%20in%