the%20government's%20%248.9%20billion%20investment%20in%20Intel%20is%20%26quot%3Bweird.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20cronyism%20in%20some%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20CNBC.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20investment%20is%20primarily%20funded%20by%20the%20CHIPS%20Act%2C%20which%20supports%20domestic%20chip%20production.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Lonsdale%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Palantir%20and%20founding%20partner%20of%20Austin-based%20venture%20capital%20firm%208VC%2C%20said%20Thursday%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Buncomfortable%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20government's%20%248.9%20billion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintel-donald-trump-buy-stake-us-other-companies-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvestment%20in%20Intel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20weird%2C%20of%20course%2C%20for%20the%20government%20to%20be%20taking%20a%20stake%20in%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Lonsdale%20said%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20CNBC's%20Squawk%20Box.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20a%20little%20bit%20weird%20for%20the%20government%20to%20be%20giving%20%249%20billion%20to%20a%20company%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20cronyism%20in%20some%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20Cronyism%2C%20the%20milder%20cousin%20of%20nepotism%2C%20is%20the%20practice%20of%20giving%20jobs%20and%20benefits%20to%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20funds%20are%20coming%20in%20part%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchips-act-bill-to-boost-us-chipmaking-competition-with-china-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20CHIPS%20and%20Science%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%202022%20law%20that%20provides%20%2452%20billion%20in%20subsidies%20and%20tax%20incentives%20to%20encourage%20domestic%20chip%20production%20and%20factory%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntel%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bgovernment's%20equity%20stake%20will%20be%20funded%20by%20the%20remaining%20