0why%20I%20want%20parents%20to%20observe%20their%20children.%20Think%20about%20%3Cem%3Ewhy%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethey%20are%20doing%20what%20they%20are%20doing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013-1756995112-500x684.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013-1756995112-500x684.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013-1756995112-219x300.jpeg%20219w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013-1756995112-768x1051.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013-1756995112-150x205.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013-1756995112.jpeg%20830w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496544%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22684%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%20changed%20Harpreet%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20his%20daughter%20greatly%2C%20who%20spent%20the%20first%20two%20years%20of%20her%20life%20in%20a%20daycare.%20But%20after%20she%20turned%20three%20and%20started%20attending%20school%2C%20Harpreet%20made%20sure%20that%20all%20his%20time%20was%20spent%20with%20her.%20Another%20thing%20he%20changed%20was%20staying%20away%20from%20the%20carrot%20and%20stick%20approach%20(using%20rewards%20and%20punishment%20to%20encourage%20de