%80%9CIt%20creates%20healthy%20competition%20and%20pride.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChoices%20that%20change%20lives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreventing%20teenage%20pregnancies%2C%20especially%20among%20already-married%20girls%2C%20became%20the%20next%20focus%20for%20Mission%20Sankalp.%20A%20list%20of%20eligible%20couples%20was%20drawn%20up%2C%20and%20they%20were%20counselled%20using%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccafeteria%20approach%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20a%20unique%20idea%20that%20puts%20every%20contraceptive%20option%20on%20the%20table%20and%20allows%20couples%20to%20make%20their%20own%20informed%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20officials%20even%20began%20attending%20weddings%20of%20legally%20married%20couples%2C%20handing%20over%20%E2%80%9Cnewlywed%20kits%E2%80%9D%20with%20reproductive%20health%20leaflets%2C%20contraceptive%20samples%2C%20and%20family%20planning%20information.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20a%20simple%20leaflet%20at%20the%20right%20time%20can%20delay%20a%20pregnancy%20and%20change%20a%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaiswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-1-1756816914.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mission%20Sankalp%20has%20certified%2010%20villages%20child%20marriage-free.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-1-1756816914.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-1-1756816914-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-1-1756816914-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-