s%20%E2%80%94%20and%20into%20that%20gap%20fall%20many%20children.%20When%20we%20encounter%20diversity%2C%20we%20often%20skirt%20around%20it%2C%20ignore%20it%2C%20label%20it%2C%20or%20respond%20with%20cruelty.%20Thus%20emerges%20the%20divide%20between%20neurotypical%20and%20neurodivergent%20children%20%E2%80%94%20another%20round%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cus%20and%20them%E2%80%9D%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-19-at-5.54.41-PM_11zon-1756817017-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20learn%20and%20heal%20and%20grow%20when%20playing%20-%20so%20can%20the%20parents!%5Cn%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-19-at-5.54.41-PM_11zon-1756817017-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-19-at-5.54.41-PM_11zon-1756817017-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-19-at-5.54.41-PM_11zon-1756817017-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-19-at-5.54.41-PM_11zon-1756817017-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-19-at-5.54.41-PM_11zon-1756817017-900x1200.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-19-at-5.54.41-PM_11zon-1756817017-600x800.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-19-at-5.54.41-PM_11zon-1756817017-450x600.jpeg%20450w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-19-at-5.54.41-PM_11zon-1756