5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Parenting%20need%20not%20be%20pure%20leading%3B%20it%20can%20just%20be%20about%20walking%20together%2C%20guiding%20each%20other%3B%20Photo%20courtesy%20Pooja%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shelja%20Sen%20sees%20a%20direct%20link%20between%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20neurodivergence%20and%20the%20mother%E2%80%99s%20depression.%20%E2%80%9CAnything%20the%20mother%20does%20or%20has%20done%20is%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20so%20much%20guilt%20and%20shame%20is%20being%20carried%20by%20the%20mother.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20family%20sessions%2C%20she%20tries%20to%20rebalance%20the%20load%2C%20asking%20fathers%20not%20only%2C%20%E2%80%98How%20are%20you%20taking%20care%20of%20your%20child%3F%E2%80%99%20but%20also%2C%20%E2%80%98How%20are%20you%20taking%20care%20of%20her%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwaati%20does%20the%20same%20with%20her%20peers.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20know%20how%20conversations%20always%20start%20with%20the%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20I%20always%20make%20it%20a%20point%20to%20ask%20the%20mothers%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20does%20your%20child%20like%2C%20what%20does%20(s)he%20enjoy%20doing%2C%20where%20is%20the%20joy%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20many%2C%20the%20mother%20also%20ends%20up%20showing%20the%20way.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Aadi%20had%20been%20neurotypical%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20bothered%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20things%2C%20including%20my%20own%20therapy.%20Because%20I%20was%20pushed%20to%20a%20corner%2C%20because%20things%20got%20dark%2C%20I%20had%20to.%20So%20I%E2%80%99m%20thankful%20now%20because%20it%20has%20made%20me%20a%20better%20parent%2C%20and%20a%20more%20aware%2C%20better%20person%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Swaati.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru-based%20play%20therapist%20and%20parenting%20coach%20Manju%